Rapid-Fire Command Questions

How do you find the size of a specific directory in human-readable format without listing all subdirectories?
---> du -sh /path/tp/directory

What command shows you the open ports and the processes listening on them?
---> ss -tunlp    or netstat -tunlp

How do you permanently append /opt/custom/bin to your $PATH?
---> echo 'export PATH=$PATH:/opt/custom/bin' >> ~/.bashrc

What is the difference between >  and >> in shell redirection?
---> '>' is for override the content, >> is for append the content

How do you find files modified exactly 3 days ago?
---> find . -type f -mtime 3